==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Riddler
<hw>Rid"dler</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who speaks in, or propounds,
riddles.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>The Riddler</b></col> <mark>[Capitalized]</mark> <cd>A
fictional character in the Batman comic books series and also in the
Batman series of movies. He was an enemy of Batman who proposed
riddles.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Riddling</ent>⟦br⟧
